---
By: Hazrat Inayat Khan
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 46
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Change
---
He who expects to change the world will be disappointed; he must change his
view. When this is done, the tolerance will come, forgiveness will come and
there will be nothing he cannot bear.
